SYNQDRIVE PHASE 2 DATABASE SCHEMA

Goal:
Design production‑ready PostgreSQL schema.

Principles:
- multi tenant
- organization isolation
- product licensing aware
- operational vehicle intelligence

------------------------------------------------
CORE TABLE GROUPS
------------------------------------------------

Organizations
Organization Memberships
Users
Stations
Products
Organization Products
Vehicles
DIMO Mirrored Vehicles
Vehicle Battery Specs
Vehicle Tire Setups
Vehicle Tire Measurements
Vehicle Brake Reference Specs
Vehicle Service Events
Vehicle Enrichment Jobs
Integrations
Organization Integrations
Billing
Prospects
Customers
Bookings

------------------------------------------------
ORGANIZATIONS
------------------------------------------------

organizations

Fields:
id
company_name
business_type
address
city
country
status
created_at
updated_at

------------------------------------------------
MEMBERSHIPS
------------------------------------------------

organization_memberships

Fields:
user_id
organization_id
role
station_scope
status

------------------------------------------------
